	</li></ul></div></div></header><div class="article-progress" data-behavior="article_progress"><div class="article-progress__bar"></div><div class="article-grid-outer container"><div class="article-grid"><aside class="article-grid__share"><div class="share-box tooltip-outer"><div style="overflow: hidden"><ul class="share-box__inner"><li class="share-box__inner__item"><a href="#" data-sharer-url="http://www.facebook.com/sharer/sharer.php?p[url]=https://www.scientificamerican.com/article/neuroscientists-discover-a-new-way-to-cross-the-blood-brain-barrier/?wt.mc=SA_Facebook-Share" class="share-box__inner__item__link" data-social-provider="Facebook" data-behavior="sharer tooltip" data-tooltip-hover data-tooltip-top data-tooltip-width="225" data-tooltip-id="facebook-tooltip"><span class="icon icon__facebook--black"></span></a></li><li class="share-box__inner__item"><a href="#" class="share-box__inner__item__link" data-social-provider="Twitter" data-behavior="sharer tooltip" data-sharer-url="https://twitter.com/intent/tweet?url=https://www.scientificamerican.com/article/neuroscientists-discover-a-new-way-to-cross-the-blood-brain-barrier/?wt.mc=SA_Twitter-Share&amp;text=Neuroscientists Discover a New Way to Cross the Blood–Brain Barrier&amp;hashtags=science" data-tooltip-hover data-tooltip-top data-tooltip-width="208" data-tooltip-id="twitter-tooltip"><span class="icon icon__twitter--black"></span></a></li><li class="share-box__inner__item"><a href="#" class="share-box__inner__item__link" data-social-provider="Reddit" data-behavior="sharer tooltip" data-sharer-url="http://www.reddit.com/submit?url=https://www.scientificamerican.com/article/neuroscientists-discover-a-new-way-to-cross-the-blood-brain-barrier/%3Fwt.mc=SA_Reddit-Share" data-tooltip-hover data-tooltip-top data-tooltip-width="208" data-tooltip-id="reddit-tooltip"><span class="icon icon__reddit--black"></span></a></li><li class="share-box__inner__item"><a href="#" class="share-box__inner__item__link" data-social-